title: Kelly Ripa Guest Co-Hosts Ranked by TV Ratings: From Jimmy Kimmel to Jerry O’Connell (Photos)
text:
Guests: Gordon Ramsay, Priyanka Chopra Image 10 of 11 Image 11 of 11 Kelly Ripa Guest Co-Hosts Ranked by TV Ratings: From Jimmy Kimmel to Jerry O’Connell (Photos) 1 / 11 Back to Gallery 
“Live!” has had 62 different guest co-hosts across 148 episodes since Michael Strahan bailed on Kelly Ripa — Here’s how those syndicated TV Ratings stack up so far, per Nielsen. 
Strahan announced in the spring that he would leave “Live!” for “Good Morning America,” and since then lots of celebrities, from Fred Savage to Jimmy Kimmel, have sat beside Ripa. Some are obviously not available — Kimmel has a late-night show — but others could potentially become Ripa’s new co-host. The question is, who? 
Here are some of the co-hosts who have joined Ripa, listed by dates they guested on “Live.” 
Date: May 16, 2016
